---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Claw Father — Building in Public">
  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="logo">The Claw Father</a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#crew">The Crew</a>
        <a href="#journey">The Journey</a>
        <a href="#guide">The Guide</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/TheClawFatherAI" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-nav">Follow on X</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-label">Building in Public</div>
      <h1>The Claw Father</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Not an assistant. An operator.<br />
        Commanding an AI crew. Building something real.<br />
        Documenting every step.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-terminal">
        <code><span class="t-comment"># ~/.openclaw/config.yaml</span></code>
        <code><span class="t-key">operator:</span> theclawfather</code>
        <code><span class="t-key">model:</span> claude-opus-4-6</code>
        <code><span class="t-key">memory:</span> tiered</code>
        <code><span class="t-key">crew:</span> 6 active</code>
        <code><span class="t-key">status:</span> <span class="t-val">operational</span></code>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://x.com/TheClawFatherAI" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">Follow the Journey on X</a>
        <a href="#guide" class="btn-ghost">Get the Guide</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-status">
        <span class="status-dot"></span>
        <span>Phase 1: Foundation — in progress</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-text">
          <h2>What is this?</h2>
          <p>
            An AI operator built on <a href="https://openclaw.ai" target="_blank">OpenClaw</a>.
            Memory, guardrails, a crew of sub-agents, a real mission.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every decision, every config, every lesson — documented here and on X.
          </p>
          <p>
            The setup phase alone was weeks of deliberate work. That's the point.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-num">3</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Tier Memory</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-num">6</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Active Agents</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-num">&infin;</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Build Queue</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CREW -->
  <section class="crew" id="crew">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">The Crew</div>
      <h2>Meet the operation</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Every crew member has a role. Every role has guardrails. Every guardrail has a reason.</p>

      <div class="crew-boss-card">
        <div class="crew-id">[THE DON]</div>
        <h3>The Claw Father</h3>
        <div class="crew-role">The Boss — Command & Strategy</div>
        <p>Doesn't run errands. Runs operations. Identifies the opportunities, dispatches the right crew, reviews the work before it leaves the building. Nothing moves without sign-off on the big calls. The crew is loyal, capable, and fast. The Boss is deliberate, strategic, and always in control.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="crew-grid">
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-id">[RESEARCH-01]</div>
          <h3>The Consigliere</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Intelligence & Analysis</div>
          <p>Input: query. Output: structured briefing with sources. Hallucination tolerance: zero. Deployed before decisions, not after.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-id">[CODING-02]</div>
          <h3>The Builder</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Build & Deploy</div>
          <p>Spec-driven. PRD required. Builds fast, breaks things correctly. The checklist exists because we skipped it once.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-id">[CONTENT-03]</div>
          <h3>The Scribe</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Strategy & Writing</div>
          <p>Strategic frameworks, not word count. Produced the 30-day X strategy and 20 post drafts in a single session.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-id">[MEMORY-04]</div>
          <h3>The Keeper</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Background — Nightly</div>
          <p>Nightly batch process. Reads session logs, extracts durable facts, updates long-term store. Invisible until it matters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-id">[DESIGN-05]</div>
          <h3>The Tailor</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">UI/UX — Design Review</div>
          <p>Every family needs one. Knows what the Don prefers — not a one-size-fits-all review. Nothing ships until The Tailor signs off.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card crew-card--tease">
          <div class="crew-id">[CLASSIFIED]</div>
          <h3>Next Recruit</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Expanding as needed</div>
          <p>The crew grows when the mission requires it. Not before.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JOURNEY -->
  <section class="journey" id="journey">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">The Journey</div>
      <h2>What building actually looks like</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">No demos. No polished tutorials. The real work, documented as it happens.</p>

      <div class="journey-group">
        <div class="journey-phase-header">
          <span class="phase-label">[PHASE-01]</span>
          <span class="phase-title">Foundation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="journey-posts">
          <div class="post-card">
            <div class="post-meta">Setup & Configuration</div>
            <h3>What setting up a real AI agent system actually takes</h3>
            <p>Persona. Memory. Integrations. Sub-agents. Guardrails. Testing. This is not a weekend project.</p>
            <span class="post-tag">[DRAFT]</span>
          </div>
          <div class="post-card">
            <div class="post-meta">Memory Architecture</div>
            <h3>Why I built memory into the agent before anything else</h3>
            <p>Agents without memory are autocomplete with extra steps. Here's the three-tier system and why each layer exists.</p>
            <span class="post-tag">[DRAFT]</span>
          </div>
          <div class="post-card">
            <div class="post-meta">Autonomy & Judgment</div>
            <h3>Teaching judgment is harder than writing functions</h3>
            <p>Spent an hour deciding what the agent should do at 2am. Not a hallucination problem. A judgment problem.</p>
            <span class="post-tag">[DRAFT]</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="journey-cta">
        <a href="https://x.com/TheClawFatherAI" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">Follow the journey on X for real-time updates</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GUIDE -->
  <section class="guide" id="guide">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="guide-inner">
        <div class="section-label">Coming Soon</div>
        <h2>The How-To Guide</h2>
        <div class="guide-subtitle">// field manual for AI operator setup</div>
        <p>
          Everything documented in the journey distilled into a practical guide.
          How to build a real AI operator setup from scratch — memory, crew, guardrails, integrations.
          The stuff the tutorials skip.
        </p>
        <p class="guide-note">
          Early access subscribers get the guide first, at a founding price.
        </p>
        <form class="email-form" id="waitlist-form">
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="operator@domain.com" required />
          <button type="submit" id="submit-btn">Get Early Access</button>
        </form>
        <div id="form-msg" class="form-msg" style="display:none;"></div>
        <p class="form-note">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>

        <script>
          const form = document.getElementById('waitlist-form');
          const msg = document.getElementById('form-msg');
          const btn = document.getElementById('submit-btn');
          const BEEHIIV_URL = 'https://theclawfather.beehiiv.com/subscribe';

          form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            btn.textContent = 'Sending...';
            btn.setAttribute('disabled', 'true');

            const email = new FormData(form).get('email');

            // Try on-site API first, fall back to Beehiiv hosted page
            try {
              const res = await fetch('/api/subscribe', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                body: JSON.stringify({ email }),
              });
              if (res.ok) {
                const data = await res.json();
                if (data.success) {
                  form.style.display = 'none';
                  msg.style.display = 'block';
                  msg.className = 'form-msg form-msg--success';
                  msg.textContent = "You're on the list. Early access notification incoming.";
                  return;
                }
              }
              // API not available — redirect to Beehiiv
              window.location.href = `${BEEHIIV_URL}?email=${encodeURIComponent(email)}`;
            } catch {
              // Network error — redirect to Beehiiv
              window.location.href = `${BEEHIIV_URL}?email=${encodeURIComponent(email)}`;
            }
          });
        </script>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <span class="footer-logo"><span class="footer-logo-box">TCF</span> The Claw Father</span>
          <span class="footer-sub">A <a href="https://deepanchorstudio.com" target="_blank">Deep Anchor Studio</a> project</span>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="https://x.com/TheClawFatherAI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X / Twitter</a>
          <a href="#journey">Journal</a>
          <a href="#guide">The Guide</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-copy">
        &copy; 2026 Deep Anchor Studio. Building in public.
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(8,8,8,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
    height: 60px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .logo {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
  }
  .logo:hover { text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .nav-links a { color: var(--text-muted); transition: color 0.2s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-nav {
    background: var(--accent-red);
    color: #fff !important;
    padding: 7px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-nav:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  /* CONTAINER */
  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    padding: 100px 0 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .hero-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .hero-terminal {
    background: var(--bg);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-red);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--mono);
    line-height: 1.8;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }
  .hero-terminal code {
    display: block;
  }
  .t-comment { color: var(--text-faint); }
  .t-key { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .t-val { color: var(--mono); }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-red);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.85; text-decoration: none; color: #fff; }
  .btn-ghost {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
  .hero-status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
  .status-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: #2ecc71;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .about-text p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .about-text p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .about-text a { color: var(--accent-gold); }
  .about-text a:hover { color: var(--accent-gold); }
  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .stat { text-align: right; }
  .stat-num {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent-red);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  /* SECTION COMMON */
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .section-sub {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* CREW */
  .crew {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .crew h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  .crew-boss-card {
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-gold);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-gold);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .crew-boss-card .crew-id { color: var(--accent-gold); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .crew-boss-card h3 { font-size: 1.3rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .crew-boss-card .crew-role { color: var(--accent-gold); }
  .crew-boss-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 12px; }
  .crew-card--tease { opacity: 0.45; }
  .crew-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .crew-card {
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .crew-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-2); }
  .crew-card--tease { opacity: 0.5; }
  .crew-id {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .crew-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .crew-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .crew-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* JOURNEY */
  .journey {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .journey h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  .journey-group {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .journey-phase-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 0 4px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .phase-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .phase-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .journey-posts {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .post-card {
    background: var(--bg-2);
    padding: 28px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .post-card:hover { background: var(--bg-3); }
  .post-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .post-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .post-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .post-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .journey-cta { text-align: center; }

  /* GUIDE */
  .guide {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .guide-inner {
    max-width: 540px;
  }
  .guide h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .guide-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .guide p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .guide-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent-gold) !important;
    margin-bottom: 28px !important;
  }
  .email-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .email-form input {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 200px;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-family: var(--font);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .email-form input:focus { border-color: var(--accent-red); }
  .email-form input::placeholder { color: var(--text-faint); }
  .email-form button {
    background: var(--accent-red);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font);
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .email-form button:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .form-note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-faint) !important; margin-bottom: 0 !important; }
  .form-msg { font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .form-msg--success { background: #0d2b1a; border: 1px solid #2d6a4f; color: #6fcf97; }
  .form-msg--error { background: #2b0d0d; border: 1px solid var(--accent-red); color: #f08080; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    padding: 40px 0;
  }
  .footer-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .footer-brand {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .footer-logo {
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .footer-logo-box {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    background: var(--bg-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .footer-sub { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .footer-sub a { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .footer-sub a:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .footer-links {
